imdb.plot outline: Alex Reed takes every day as it comes. He works for a special clandestine operations group known as Arcane, and along with his fellow agent, Andy, they're thrown into all manner of morally questionable situations and are expected to grit their teeth and power through. The consequences of their actions begin to weigh on their conscience as their lives are whittled down again and again.
